{
  "stem": "15115.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Birkenau?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, Birkenau was the biggest brutality that you ever seen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I didn't go through it my-- personally.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I've seen people, first of all, lot of people tried to escape.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No escape out of Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They put the dogs at night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They go over there, and they bring them in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you used to hang them right in front of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had to wait about sometimes two, three hours until everybody, you know-- after you're working the whole day long, you have to wait two, three hours till the-- everything is organized.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they take the guy and they hang them, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Or during the war days, you know, during a day's work, somebody would take your number.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You will-- for some reason or other you didn't do the work right and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They bring you over to the-- when you come into the camp, they call your number.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Put you in a-- in a big bank, a big chair like this, put your head inside, and give you 25 up your ass, you know, with a big-- there was-- quite often, because from different commanders, you know, it was done this way.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as you mentioned, the music.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The music was when we used to go in the morning and we used to be-- mutze up, mutze up, you know, take your hats, you know, walking, you know.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we passed through the gates.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then at night the same thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We used to have the music playing as we're coming into-- what do you call?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was-- if it was no delays, you know, nobody run away or nothing like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we were going to-- we used to go right into the camp, like into our blocks.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
